{"tid":1204132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好人好姐邊會做毅進仔","createTime":"2019-06-11T14:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T14:29:22.000Z","uid":76364,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e508a431b0a114483a4f680ea126a9c415993408","tid":1204132,"uid":76364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:19:28.000Z","msg":"唔好怪毅進仔啦 其實佢地仲係小學生黎 <br />\n我係佢地表哥 唔係好親個隻 <br />\n佢地有少少低智個d唔好講啦 <br />\n佢地讀特殊學校個d都無謂提 <br />\n不過大家放過佢地啦 佢地仲係讀緊小三 <br />\n佢地老豆老母都好辛苦 要照顧毅進仔<br />\n佢地細細個已經食雞唔食雞皮 食橙食埋橙皮 <br />\n我代佢地係呢度向大家道歉一聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家聽日齊心，一齊向住同一個目標前進"},{"pid":"d40fef7b287b21927fba6a96883213472076176f","tid":1204132,"uid":229508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:23:03.000Z","msg":"毅進狗"},{"pid":"37c30e9f7bbfc3269d51852bd1d9d9013f9c1530","tid":1204132,"uid":227026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:24:36.000Z","msg":"你試下無狗糧出佢地會點<br />\n犬改不了吃屎"},{"pid":"176027c6585ddde0ed2914623466e93025dedd44","tid":1204132,"uid":76364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37c30e9f7bbfc3269d51852bd1d9d9013f9c1530","tid":1204132,"uid":227026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:24:36.000Z","msg":"你試下無狗糧出佢地會點<br />\n犬改不了吃屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:27:21.000Z","msg":"佢地會即刻反埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e86578d56eaa9c08f1c5110710307fbc6f1342","tid":1204132,"uid":87116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"海外港人支援流亡義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1204022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1204022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}